Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,13,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,13,,Did you ever experience it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,13,,Two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,13,,A startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,13,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,13,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,13,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,13,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,13,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
