Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:29.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\b1\pos(648.649,466.667)\blur0.667\bord0\an4} alucardnoyuuutsu \N Anonymous{trumann#7436} \N Ziusudra \N Perevodildo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he Hikaru Genji or Narihira?{光源氏か業平か - It could be saying this bec}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The super-handsome Sublieutenant receives mountains of love letters every day,{超ドハンサムのshouiには毎日山のラブ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,however, among those there is someone different from the other girls,{だがその中の何物かとshouiは デートの約束を}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with whom he makes a date in secret.{密かにそっと取り交わし}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In an attempt to protect our High Collar Lady,{そこでハイカラさんを守ろうと}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,these two mad lads decide to tail Shinobu.{2人はshouiの尾行を決議した}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But due to Benio's unawareness, Ushigorou's plan fails{だが何も知らない紅緒のために牛五郎の尾行は失敗し}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and she happens to stumble across Shinobu's date of all things!{こともあろうに少尉のデートの現場を目撃する羽目に なろうとは}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she a fool for being trustful? Or is the deceiving side in the wrong?{信じた自分がバカなのか騙す向こうが悪い}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is troubled and can't sleep anymore. When will the truth come to light?{ちょっぴり眠れのハイカラさんこの真相は いつ晴れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This hurt more than I had expected,{これは思っていたより重傷だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something about it...{なんとかしなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bummer that we have to be the first to wake up in here.{私達ってお屋敷中で一番早く起きなきゃ ならないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough, isn't it?{辛いわよねー}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?\NHowever, I'm sure that good things await us.{そうねでもそのうちにきっと何かいいこと あるわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?{何かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Ranko exercising.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Let's have her teach us!{さね私たちも教わりましょうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you teach us how to ex-{体操教えー}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for disturbing you.{失礼しました}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought it was Ranko...{蘭子さんだとばっかり}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{いいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wanna try?{どうやってみる}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No worries!{とんでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our apologies!{失礼}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Working out truly washes all troubles away!{悩み事はは一汗描くのが一番だわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:00.45,Sign,,0,0,100,,{\c&HEBE2E7&\b1\blur0.667\bord0}Episode 21 \N {\fs46.667} Life is Short, Yet Riddled with Worries {命みじかく悩み果てなく}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious. Benio will surely like it.{おいしそう、Benioさん喜ぶの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?{なんと}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After{だってbenioさんは朝っぱらから体操なんかして}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll definitely be hungry.{お腹を減らしてるに違いないんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be yet another lively morning!{今朝また格別に気分の良い朝でございます ね}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach feels heavy and my chest hurts!{胃が重い、胸が痛む}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, aren't you eating?{Benio様朝ごはんは}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood,{いらないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like eating.{食べたくないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But not eating will be no good for your health.{でも食べなきゃ体に毒いいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.{いいのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.57,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong, Benio?{どうしたのじゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually eat three bowls of rice first thing in the morning,{朝もはよから三杯飯をかっ食らうお前が}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,did you scavenge and eat something bad?{何か悪いものでも拾い食いしたのではないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I sincerely apologise{悪かったですね、あたしだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for not being hungry all the time!{食欲減退することくらいあります}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so mad!{イライラする}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be well.{ どうも元気がないようですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...{信じられませんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the omen for an incoming calamity!{これは天変地異の前触れかもしれんぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not an earthquake, though.{お地震でも起らねばよいが}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out,{よしてよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,why are you joking about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you should worry more about her!{皆真面目に心配してよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What might have happened to her?{benioさん本当にどうしちゃったのかしら }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet I swore that{あんな人のこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't think about him.{何とも思ってなかったはずなのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the reason I lost my appetite.{食欲減退イライラの原因が歩いてきたわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?{どうしたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to school without eating{何も食べずに学校へ行くの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,won't be good for your health.{体に良くないです}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you at least drink some milk?{ミルクだけでも飲んでいったらえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boom!{ドカー}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, leave me alone!{ほっといてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep calm when I see your face!{あなたの顔見るとあたし平静じゃいられなくなるんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone, don't look at me!{ほっといて、顔を見てないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened now?{どうかしたのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like she doesn't like me.{どうも嫌われているらしいですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly hurts my pride.{自信なくなりますね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I{僕はこれでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,have always been popular among girls.{そんなに女の子に人気のない方じゃなかったんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover,{それに}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been serious, yet she hasn't got any closer to me.{これだけ真面目な気持ちで近づいたこともなかったのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a while{彼女と出会って}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,since I first met her,{もう随分なるのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but that bird keeps flying away from my arms.{どうしても腕の中から逃げていくあの小鳥 - you decide whether to keep the metaphor or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, let's finally go back to school.{Ushigorou久しぶりで学校へやってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At your service!{合点承知}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine, having skipped breakfast?{朝食抜きで大丈夫なの}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all good.{へいきよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! You've done your homework this time, have you?{親分宿題はしてあるんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about homework right now,{宿題なんてこの際どっちでもいいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy just to breath some fresh air{この家から少しでも遠く離れて}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and meet up with all of my classmates again.{久しぶりにクラスメイトの顔でも見れば 元気出るわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.{さやってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems in a bad shape.{なんだかひどく参ってるみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried... What should I do?{心配だなどうしよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, I'll accompany you to school.{その日まで一応同じで一緒に行きましょう - not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hell no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you go faster?{もっと早く走れないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to increase your speed!{もっとスピードは出せないのかって言ってるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, but just so you know, it'll be real fast,{そりゃね 足が自慢のこのushigorou}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so try not to fly away!{いくらだって飛ばしますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou! Faster! Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's avoiding me after all.{やはり僕を避けている}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you going with Benio?{なぜbenioさんと一緒に行かないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my intention,{こっちはその気だったんだが}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like she just loathes me.{すっかり紅緒さんに嫌われたようで}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why aren't you following her?{じゃあどうして後を追わないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, I'll just end up hurting her more instead.{そんなことをしたらかえってあの人を傷つけるだけだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!{噓}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd put my life on the line{僕は好きな人のためなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and chase the person I love no matter how far.{命がけで地の果て まで追ってゆく}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Benio was hoping that you'd chase her.{Benioさんも きっと少尉が追ってくるのを待っていた はずなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...{まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't understand such a simple thing,{それくらいのことがわからないんなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't deserve your playboy title.{プレイボーイの看板を外してよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down, Benio...{benioさんの心の中は}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks about nothing but you.{心の中はshouiのことでいっぱいなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This...{だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why she tells you she hates you.{だから嫌だっていう言葉も出てくるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't understand such a simple thing,{それくらいのことわからないんなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,hands off Benio!{benioさんから手を引いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot... Idiot...\NUshigorou, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, did ya say somethin'?{親分なんかおっしゃいましたか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to go faster, but why did you actually do it?{早く走れっていうのになぜ早く走るのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What're ya trynna say?{そんなん無茶な}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I always follow your orders...{あしゃいつだって言いつけ通りに}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not seeing the point!{だからだからっていうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that we should've been side by side with him.{shouiと並んで走りたくなかったわけでも ないのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I was supposed to speed up, right?{なら飛ばせなんて言わなきゃよいがしょうに}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. But I didn't want you to run fast either...{だってだって何も人の言う通りに飛ばすこともないじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya want me to go faster?{いってあしゃ飛ばしゃいいんですかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did ya want me to go at a slower pace? Just tell me!{それとものるのろ歩きゃいいんですかどっちなんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand?{そんなことがわからないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get ya at all.{まるっきりわかりません}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You obstinate henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it!{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You have {\i1}that thing{\i0} for Shinobu!{ 親分はshouiに ほの字でやんすね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!{いやね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's you, teacher!{あら、先生}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, good morning. \NOh, right, it's been a long while.{先生、おはようございます。あら、いいえ。暫くでした}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, it's truly been a long time.{そういえばお久しぶりの投稿ですわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is why I'm feeling so nostalgic!{でもそのせいかとっても懐かしいです}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura being nostalgic? This must be a devilish omen.{花村さんなつかしがるなんて、朝っぱらから縁起でもない}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.62,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)\c&H292922&\3c&HE0E7DB&}Righteous path towards wifehood
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope nothing bad happens today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!{おはよう、皆様}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ages!{お久しぶり}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't gone to school in a while, haven't you?{このところずっと学校いらっしゃらなかったでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot happened...{色々とあったもんで}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I'm here today,{でもせっかく来たんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,let's celebrate with some anmitsu!{パートうさばらしにあんみつも}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I have to go straight home.{あのそれが帰りに道草くってられないの私}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why so?{ほらどうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Osono was officially betrothed.{Osonoさんねお輿入れが決まったのよほら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not just me, Kanoko too.{でも私だけじゃないのよKanokoさんも}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otei too.{I think it's Otei...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Shizuko and Matsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we can't waste any time eating anmitsu.{というわけでみんなここのところあんみつに足が届いてるのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!{ごめんあそばせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Osono, when will you get married?{Osomeさんところで公式はいつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, before asking others, tell us about yourself!{あら人のことを聞く前に ご自分の薄情なさったらどうなの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, who was the first to be engaged?{ねえねえ 誰が一番早いかしら - I thought it could also be "who will be the first to get married", but it mismatches with the next line at 13:47}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuko, right?{静子さんじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think it was Kanoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget Matsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Shizuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:22.22,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(250,450)\b0\blur0.667\3c&HCF6111&} Kyaa kyaa kyaa \NWow-wow \NEenie, meenie, miney, moe... {honestly, no clue what's this ぺ／ワ４わ／ね／か thing, but pe*ne-wa*ne sounds like some children's rhytm so I went with this}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuya for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a short while since I last came to school,{ほんのしばらく学校に来ないうちに}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:30.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000100&\fade(0,0)\b0\blur0.667\3c&HCD5D0F&} Left out {solitarily; in a lonely fashion; all alone; by oneself}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it feels like I've been left behind.{私バスに乗り遅れてしまったみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How miserable...{みじめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for all of us to decide our path.{みんな進路が決まっていく時期なのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll graduate soon, after all.{もうすぐ女学校も卒業ですもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that long face?{何さえない顔してんのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're marrying Ijuuin, aren't you?{あなたは伊集院にお嫁に行くんでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding who was the first to be engaged... Wasn't it Benio?{一番先にお話が決まったのは紅緒じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It was her!{よそうだったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:03.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H332B1C&\b1\blur0.667\c&HD2D7D0&}Wifehood {the same word as on the sign}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay everyone, before checking your homework, I want to talk about something.{さて、本日は宿題を提出していただく前に一言}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since many of you are brides-to-be by now,{立つの日を近くに控えた女性の道について}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to give you some suggestions.{申し述べたいと思います}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kobayashi?{小林さんなんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, while giving us academic advice{はいあの普段についての有益なお話をしていただくのも}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,could indeed be profitable,{大変結構だと思いますが}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be better to listen to the stories{それよりも私たちは経験者から}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ones that already have experience{事実に即した生活の記録を}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to receive concrete information.{聞かせていただきたいのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to share experiences, {経験談を}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you're out of luck!{a bit personalised + italian as I couldn't understand clearly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my heart and soul into teaching,{教育に精神を捧げて}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so, as an unmarried woman,{今だ独身の私には}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the position to tell you anything!{何も語る資格はない}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, don't let yourself down.{先生ひがまないでください}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right,{そうなんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean to ask you,{先生のことは 諦めるとして}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we have an apprentice bride in this class,{このクラスには見習い花嫁として}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who lives at his husband-to-be's house.{嫁ぎ先住み込んでいる}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the expert in here!{その道の大先輩}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...{そんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, then...{なるほどそれで}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear Hanamura's experience first-hand!{はなむらさんその生々しい 体験談を聞きたいのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, tell us more!{べにお聞かせて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, please share your valuable experience.{花村さんでは貴重なる体験談をどうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I... I...{あの私あたし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you call your future husband?{未来のハズバンドをなんと呼びかもうや}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you held his hand?{手は握ったりよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you kissed him?{口づけは}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mwah, mwah!{接吻}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Hanamura, tell us candidly{いつも活発な花村さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,everything about your animated life, {包み隠さずおしゃべりした}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you my permission.{先生が許可します}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's an order!{いいえ、命令です}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I...{私それどころじゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, tell us.{べにお、言ってよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki... why are you doing this too...{環あなたまでそんなこと}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the right to listen, after all.{だってあたしには聞く権利があるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why, don't you?{わかるでしょこのように}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, go on.{さあおっしゃって}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.{わかったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, then I'll be honest.{皆さんでは本当のことを言います}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!{早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't have any kind of personal experience...{私にはお話すべき体験談など}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you...{何一つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell you!{何一つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDEF4FC&\3c&H181E16&\blur0.667\b1}Tailoring Club {honestly no idea what's 室縫裁 but 裁縫 is "sewing" and 室 is room so either I'm stupid or they accidentally mirrored the sign; this room doesn't matter anyway and is nondescript from the inside - perevodildo // It's because for some reason they mirror many signs in this series, like they mirrored "restaurant" in one of the previous episodes - alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu with a geisha?{忍さんの芸者と}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...{信じられないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never do such things.{忍さんに限って}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you must have misunderstood something!{いいえ何かの間違いを忍さんはあなたを}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I even spotted them together,{でもその人とshouiが一緒にいるところも見たし}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and she even sends him letters.{その人から手紙も来たのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!{嘘じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were a lie,{そうなら私だって}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be crying this much!{こんなに泣いたりしない}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio, so you do like Shinobu, after all.{ねえべにおあなたやっぱりしのぶさんが好きなんじゃ ない}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance! I'll never like him!{違うわそんなはずないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar, liar, liar.{嘘}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't care this much otherwise.{嫌いでそんなに慌てるもんですが}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I don't!{違うったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You crying this much just tells the truth.{泣いたりはねたりまする}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, my best friend sees through me.{流石親友私の心を見抜いてるでも}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, Shinobu likes that geisha.{でもしょういが好きなのはその芸者さんなのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You loved him too, Tamaki, didn't you?{たまきは少尉の事が好きだったんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a shock?{ ショックじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, regarding that...{それならね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already let go.{もう 諦めちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...{たまき}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to feel uneasy forever.{いつまでも ウジウジしていたくないし}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be on my own for a while{卒業したら何かやりたいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and do something that I like.{新婦人の一人としてね - I don't really understand this one, it can't be "as a bride" because it's introduced in the next sentence, but at the same time "being on her own" doesn't seem the correct translation...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I'll find somebody new to love.{そして新しい恋を探すの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is short...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall in love, maiden...{命短し恋せよ乙女 - a poem}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is elegant as usual,{相変わらず颯爽としてるなtamaki}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she hasn't lost heart at all.{ちっともクヨクヨしてなくって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, we may end up walking a different path,{benioお互いに違った道を歩くことになるか もしれないけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will both find our way to happiness regardless.{それぞれ自分の手で幸せをつかみましょうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.{わかったわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll act as if I've never met{あんなshouiのことなんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that dumbass sublieutenant!{なかったもっと私も忘れる}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again...{またそんなこと言って}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some misunderstanding about that geisha,{その芸者のことはきっと何かの間違いよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who Shinobu is, he wouldn't do that.{私にはしのぶさんって人がわかるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It really seems like she knows him better than me!{まるで 私の方がshouiのことよくわかってるみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So miserable...{私してみじめ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go the opposite way.{ 反対の方へやって}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What, aren't we goin' home now?{ええ親分家へ帰えるんじゃねんですかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!{いいから早くやって}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ijuuin mansion should be on the right,{伊集院なら左へ行くはず}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but she went to the opposite direction,{右へ行くとはこれは昔}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teacher, I cannot let this slide.{教師としてほっとおけん}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, rickshawman.{これこれ車や}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I need{頼みますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.{へいへい}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, chase that rickshaw!{うざ早くあの車を尾行して}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Chase?{尾行}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a good thing to do...{尾行穏やかじゃねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop loitering!{ガチャガチャ言ってないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!{早く}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, aight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, aight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, aight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Make haste!{急いで}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you run a bit faster, or speed up,{もっと[?]走れないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said it in a million ways!{あばよとかなんとかさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, are you planning to keep complaining from up there? Do you think anyone could do this?{お客さんにそこにふんどい帰って文句つけんなら誰にだってできんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you gotta hurry that badly, do it yourself.{そんなに急ぐんならお前さんやってみんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward, you're looking down of me just because I'm a woman?{己、女だと侮って}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's switch, then!{では交代}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.52,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\bord1.333\c&HEAE4E7&\3c&H0E163C&\blur0.667} Bonk {ボカッ - bop; pow; bonk; thump​}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away if you don't want to get crashed!{personalised}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?{しどい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really wild...{いや[?]かしらん - I don't know...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now turn right.{その先を右へ廻って}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Yanagibashi.{柳橋をやってちょうだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagibashi? Ooh, wanna beat up those Violet squad dudes?{柳橋あああのすみれ組に殴り込みでしか親分 - they appeared in episode 14 *I think* - the one in which Kichiji first appears}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.{違うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where the hell are we goin'?{ 一体どこへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we'll be meeting a geisha.{もちろん芸者遊びしてくるの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hangin' out with a geisha ain't somethin' for women!{芸者遊びなんて女のするこっちゃ誤算せん ぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see me as a woman in any case, so...{どうせ女だなんて思ってないんでしょうが}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But... ya see...{それは}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can see them!{italian, I think it's correct}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out the way!{あばよっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be going.{行ってくるわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time, Boss!{いってらっしゃいませごゆっくり}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting a geisha!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...{信じられない}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be hallucinating...{私の目の錯覚}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in?{失礼いたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle will start soon...{いよいよ戦闘開始だわははい}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening...{こんばんは}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady...{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as our High Collar Lady can be modern,{いかに新時代のhaikaraさんとても}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't hanging out with a geisha{娘だてらの芸者遊び}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit too much?{とはちと[水郷?]が過ぎないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards are laid on the table{花は紅柳は緑 - wordplay on the proverb 柳は緑花は紅 - Hana-> Hanamura, Yanagi->Yanagibashi}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and tonight there is no room for forgiveness.{今宵高等の巷に鎬を削るか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the decisive woman versus woman fight.{女と女の真剣勝負}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady is trying to clarify her bond with Shinobu,{今宵こそ少尉との関係をはっきりしようと はいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and asks Kichiji to marry Shinobu.{花のやKichijiにShouiと結婚してよと詰め寄っ た}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman-to-woman discussion gets fired up...{女と女の戦いは汁は暇なかこいのいじ.. can't understand...}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.92,0:23:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However,{がしかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what Kichiji says totally,{Kichijiの口から出たものは}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,totally exceeds Benio's expectations...{意外ないない波の上話}
